-improving-workforce-equity-outcomes</link><description>Opportunity@Work 的联合创始人兼首席执行官谈到了该非营利组织的使命，即通过其他途径为熟练工人扩大平等的职业机会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/bem/our-insights/opportunity-at-work-addressing-the-opportunity-gap-and-improving-workforce-equity-outcomes</guid></item><item><title>私募股权行业对人工智能的清晰认识</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/private-capital/our-insights/a-clear-eyed-view-of-gen-ai-for-the-private-equity-industry</link><description>私募股权公司可以通过将生成式人工智能融入其业务来达到更高的高度，但开始时需要深思熟虑的方法。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/private-capital/our-insights/a-clear-eyed-view-of-gen-ai-for-the-private-equity-industry</guid></item><item><title>伊比利亚绿色工业机遇：生物甲烷</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/the-iberian-green-industrial-opportunity-biomethane</link><description>到 2030 年，西班牙有潜力实现生物甲烷年产量达到 20 太瓦时，以帮助促进其脱碳。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/the-iberian-green-industrial-opportunity-biomethane</guid></item><item><title>伊比利亚绿色工业机遇：电气化和可再生能源</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/the-iberian-green-industrial-opportunity-electrification-and-renewables</link><description>所有利益相关者的合作可以通过电气化和可再生能源部署推动伊比利亚脱碳。在这里，我们讨论西班牙的雄心、挑战和潜力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/the-iberian-green-industrial-opportunity-electrification-and-renewables</guid></item><item><title>制造更多重要的药物</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/life-sciences/our-insights/making-more-medicines-that-matter</link><description>十年或更长时间以来，生物制药研发的生产力一直在下降。我们提出了可持续、创造价值的创新方案，即使面对行业逆风加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/life-sciences/our-insights/making-more-medicines-that-matter</guid></item><item><title>零售商的气候路线图：绘制脱碳价值链路径</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/capabilities/sustainability/our-insights/retailers-climate-road-map-charting-paths-to-decarbonized-value-chains</link><description>一般零售商的范围 3 指标中捕获的大多数排放量都是通过产品价值链产生的。这些价值链可以实现脱碳——但前提是多利益相关方采取有针对性的行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/capabilities/sustainability/our-insights/retailers-climate-road-map-charting-paths-to-decarbonized-value-chains</guid></item><item><title>作者讲座：如何获得 15 分钟的成名</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/mckinsey-on-books/author-talks-how-to-claim-your-15-minutes-of-fame</link><description>哈佛大学教授卡斯·桑斯坦 (Cass Sunstein) 探讨了文化市场、流行度和名气的本质——谁想要它、谁得到它以及如何得到它。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/mckinsey-on-books/author-talks-how-to-claim-your-15-minutes-of-fame</guid></item></channel></rss>